 national championships that summer, but she had no idea there was something called the world championships that followed if she made the team.\", \"from\": 8342, \"to\": 8525, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the national championships\", \"from\": 8379, \"to\": 8405}, {\"ngram\": \"no idea\", \"from\": 8431, \"to\": 8438}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 8449, \"to\": 8458}, {\"ngram\": \"the world championships\", \"from\": 8466, \"to\": 8489}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 8516, \"to\": 8524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She squeaked into the 200 final at the national meet, then tore her hamstring.\", \"from\": 8526, \"to\": 8604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the national meet\", \"from\": 8561, \"to\": 8578}, {\"ngram\": \"her hamstring\", \"from\": 8590, \"to\": 8603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tonja Buford-Bailey, a leading sprint coach whose team Thomas would soon join, approached her after the race and told her she needed to rehab that leg and then learn how to run the turn.\", \"from\": 8606, \"to\": 8792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8606, \"end\": 8625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonja_Buford-Bailey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tonja Buford-Bailey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonja_Buford-Bailey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonja_Buford-Bailey\"}, {\"begin\": 8661, \"end\": 8667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.986954667067403, \"rank\": 0.013216944395718558, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a leading sprint coach\", \"from\": 8627, \"to\": 8649}, {\"ngram\": \"whose team\", \"from\": 8650, \"to\": 8660}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 8706, \"to\": 8714}, {\"ngram\": \"rehab\", \"from\